text: Henry Clarke (c. 1917 – April 26, 1996) was an American fashion photographer, known particularly for his work for Vogue. Clarke was born in Los Angeles in about 1917. He died on April 26, 1996 at the Anglo-American Hospital in Le Cannet, France, at the age of 78. ==References== Category:1917 births Category:1996 deaths Category:20th-century American photographers Category:Fashion photographers
